title: Introduction
itunes:title: Introduction
description: Welcome to The HoneyDew podcast, y'all! This week I introduce/re-introduce myself, share a bit of my life story and an understanding of what this show is all about. My guest Co-Host for this ep is Josh Adam Meyers, AKA Jimmy Josh Adams, AKA The King of Fleece, AKA the 4-Legged Comedian! I'll be dewin it every #Wenzdee right here at the Your Mom's House studio. Enjoy The HoneyDew! http://TheHoneyDewPodcast.com
